    <detaileddescription>
<para>Overrides the DatabaseConnection_pgsql.</para><para>The primary purpose of this class is to allow for prefixing of Chado tables. By default the only way to support this is to add an array to the &apos;prefix&apos; key of the settings.php file. But this is problematic. For example, what if there is a contact table in the Drupal database as well as one in Chado. The default prefix replacement would always rewrite it to be the one in Chado. This class is intended to be used when the Chado tables are needed. </para>    </detaileddescription>
